# But DO track the curated brand assets we ship with the app
# (logos + favicon used by the dashboard at runtime). The
# leading `!` overrides the case-insensitive `Brand/` match
# that macOS APFS would otherwise apply to `assets/brand/`.
!assets/brand/
!assets/brand/**

